  Locus:
    Page: 433
    Verse: 7
Tags:
  - Simplicity
---
To live a life of faith in utter dependence upon God is very simple. It is
the simplest life possible. It is the only life entirely free from the
complications which afflict all those who depend upon human effort and
finite wisdom. But while it is simple, it is far from easy.
